#. type: Content of: <p>
#: ../../skycultures/tukano/description.en.utf8:30
msgid ""
"This constellation is described as the occidental Southern Cross "
"constellation. Sometimes this traditional occidental constellation also "
"means an Otter or a turtle by the Tukano people."
msgstr "この星座は西洋のみなみじゅうじ座に当たります。時にこの伝統的な西洋星座は、トゥカノの人々にとってカワウソやカメも意味します。"

#. type: Content of: <h3>
#: ../../skycultures/tukano/description.en.utf8:31
msgid "Nhorkoatero\\grupo de estrelas\\Pleiades"
msgstr "Nhorkoatero(ノルコアテロ)\\grupo de estrelas(グルポ・デ・エストレラス)\\Pleiades(プレアデス)"

#. type: Content of: <h3>
#: ../../skycultures/tukano/description.en.utf8:31
msgid "Nhorkoatero - Grupo de Estrelas - Group of Stars"
msgstr ""
"Nhorkoatero(ノルコアテロ) - Grupo de Estrelas(グルポ・デ・エストレラス) - Group of "
"Stars(星のグループ)"

#. type: Content of: <p>
#: ../../skycultures/tukano/description.en.utf8:32
msgid ""
"The translation of <em>nhorkoatero</em> is literally group of stars. "
"Identified as our Pleiades this is very significant as a time keeper within "
"a complex calendar to Tukano people. It is also used as a rainy period "
"pointer."
msgstr ""
"ノルコアテロ(<em>nhorkoatero</em>)は直訳すると「星のグループ」の意味です。この星座はプレアデスと同定され、これはトゥカノの人々にとっての複雑な暦の中でタイムキーパーとして非常に重要です。また雨期の指針としても使用されます。"

#. type: Content of: <h3>
#: ../../skycultures/tukano/description.en.utf8:33
msgid "Waikhasa\\moquém\\a kind of recipient to cook fish"
